  <section>
    <h2>Browser Support</h2>
    <p>The <code>&lt;menu&gt;</code> element is supported in all browsers. Its semantic meaning is recognized by screen readers, though the element renders identically to <code>&lt;ul&gt;</code> by default.</p>
  </section>
